title: Japanese Art Collection 2024 Wall Calendar
description:
A home and office necessity to keep track of important dates, this Wall Calendar in 12"x12" format is made with only the highest quality paper and printing methods featuring stunning, carefully-curated imagery.

  • Dimensions: 12"x 12"
  • 4 month preview page of following year
  • Each page includes before & after preview months
  • Includes public & culturally significant holiday
  • 3 languages: English, French, & Spanish
  • Pink holographic foil detail
